OL,4,CThorntons: Chocolate maker to close all
OL,5,Cshops putting 600 jobs at risk
OL,6, Chocolate maker Thorntons has said none
OL,7, of its stores will reopen after
OL,8, coronavirus lockdowns are lifted.
OL,10,FThe decision to close its 61 shops will
OL,11,Fput more than 600 jobs at risk.
OL,13,FThe company said it had been badly hit
OL,14,Fby the pandemic, which forced its
OL,15,Fstores to shut their doors during the
OL,16,Fcrucial Christmas and Easter holidays.
OL,18,F"The obstacles we have faced and will
OL,19,Fcontinue to face on the High Street are
OL,20,Ftoo severe," said Thorntons retail
OL,21,Fdirector Adam Goddard.
